                     <interp inst="t18490226-734-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 2 pence and 3 halfpence; the moneys of <persName id="t18490226-name-702" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-702" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-702" type="surname" value="WOOLFORD"></interp>
