                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-704" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS LUCKETT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 234). The prisoner was given into my charge—on the way to the station he said, "What a fool I must have been to take this 3 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>." (The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
